@UBL litellm-integration
LEXICO: #litellm #config
## Integração LiteLLM (config.yaml)

```yaml
- model_name: qwen-1.5b
  litellm_params:
    model: ollama/qwen2.5-coder:1.5b-instruct
    api_base: http://localhost:11435   # ← iGPU Intel

- model_name: qwen-3b
  litellm_params:
    model: ollama/qwen2.5-coder:3b-instruct
    api_base: http://localhost:11434   # ← RTX 3050
```



@UBL file-structure
LEXICO: #structure #paths
## Estrutura de Arquivos

```
C:\igpu\                          ← Diretório de trabalho do Ollama iGPU
  ollama.exe                      ← Symlink para ollama ipex-llm
  *.dll                           ← DLLs SYCL Intel
  start.bat                       ← Launcher simples

C:\miniforge3\                    ← Miniforge3 (conda base)
  envs\llm-cpp\                   ← Ambiente Python 3.11 com ipex-llm
    Scripts\init-ollama.bat       ← Script de inicialização oficial Intel
    Lib\site-packages\bigdl\cpp\libs\  ← binários ipex-llm Ollama

TURBOQUANT_V42\
  01_neocortex_framework\
    scripts\NC-SCR-FR-111-ollama-igpu-launcher.bat  ← launcher NC
  config.yaml                     ← LiteLLM com rotas dGPU + iGPU
```



@UBL orchestration-tier
LEXICO: #tier #routing
## Tier de Orquestração

```
neocortex_llm_router(action="route.call", complexity="OPERACIONAL")
→ qwen-1.5b (Intel iGPU :11435) — gratuito, 24/7

neocortex_llm_router(action="route.call", complexity="TECNICO")
→ deepseek-chat (Cloud via LiteLLM) — ou fallback qwen-3b (RTX 3050)

neocortex_llm_router(action="route.call", complexity="RACIOCINIO")
→ deepseek-reasoner (Cloud)
```
